Document-oriented databases are one of the main categories of so-called NoSQL databases and the popularity of the term document-oriented database has grown with the use of the term NoSQL itself. In contrast to relational databases and their notions of Relations, these systems are designed around an abstract notion of Document.The concept of database Document
